{"tid":953291,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"征途online台服結束營運","createTime":"2018-12-23T22:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T10:25:39.000Z","uid":107639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dbf605cc1bac00ca08d809ac6343cdfabf019ffa","tid":953291,"uid":107639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T22:58:46.000Z","msg":"《征途 online》自2006年推出以來，廣受眾多玩家們的喜愛，萬人上線同測、新服加開不已，遊戲中的霸業征途，幫派成員間互相扶持的點點滴滴，度過一連串有笑有淚的時光，成為每個人腦海中最深刻的回憶！一路上有大家的支持與肯定是我們莫大的榮幸。因為有您的參與及陪伴，讓《征途 online》曾創下許多亮眼佳績。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長期以來營運團隊始終秉持著當初打造遊戲的熱忱與初衷，這一路上來，衷心感激所有玩家們對《征途 online》及雷爵網絡的支持。但由於《征途 online》玩家人數一天一天的滑落，已無法支撐遊戲營運，雖然不捨，我們仍很遺憾的在此向支持《征途 online》的玩家們宣布，遊戲將於2018/12/26(三)正式結束營運。對於這決定，我們在此要向所有玩家致上最高的歉意，也再一次衷心感謝各位的支持。<br />\n<br />\n雷爵營運團隊敬上<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://member.lager.com.tw/event/zt_end\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmember.lager.com.tw%2Fevent%2Fzt_end&d=ifq9L76%2BWd08ZR2REB7OX4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b414bc19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://member.lager.com.tw/event/zt_end</a><br />\n<br />\n12月26號執la"},{"pid":"12d88b95df5da4d345ab205ae56a9ff8352999ad","tid":953291,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T23:16:24.000Z","msg":"<code>Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"bfbbc447cd4c01f82a3c13ddaaa9420204c224d9","tid":953291,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T23:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aae1c102f5b3920a4adca3a4cc9f6010ab54317","tid":953291,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T23:18:45.000Z","msg":"冇玩過，可惜已經冇得開新ac"},{"pid":"b6120fde6b01a59753bc98a44eff7739a61fe72b","tid":953291,"uid":20818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:39:49.000Z","msg":"國戰真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5fd0900e4cb